[package]
name = "iced"
description = "A cross-platform GUI library inspired by Elm"

[features]
default = [ "wgpu",]
wgpu = [ "iced_renderer/wgpu", "iced_widget/wgpu",]
image = [ "iced_widget/image", "dep:image",]
svg = [ "iced_widget/svg",]
canvas = [ "iced_widget/canvas",]
qr_code = [ "iced_widget/qr_code",]
lazy = [ "iced_widget/lazy",]
debug = [ "iced_winit/debug",]
tokio = [ "iced_futures/tokio",]
async-std = [ "iced_futures/async-std",]
smol = [ "iced_futures/smol",]
palette = [ "iced_core/palette",]
system = [ "iced_winit/system",]
web-colors = [ "iced_renderer/web-colors",]
webgl = [ "iced_renderer/webgl",]
highlighter = [ "iced_highlighter",]
multi-window = [ "iced_winit/multi-window",]
advanced = []

[workspace]
members = [ "core", "futures", "graphics", "highlighter", "renderer", "runtime", "style", "tiny_skia", "wgpu", "widget", "winit", "examples/*",]

[package.version]
workspace = true

[package.edition]
workspace = true

[package.authors]
workspace = true

[package.license]
workspace = true

[package.repository]
workspace = true

[package.homepage]
workspace = true

[package.categories]
workspace = true

[package.keywords]
workspace = true

[badges.maintenance]
status = "actively-developed"

[dependencies.iced_core]
workspace = true

[dependencies.iced_futures]
workspace = true

[dependencies.iced_renderer]
workspace = true

[dependencies.iced_widget]
workspace = true

[dependencies.iced_winit]
features = [ "application",]
workspace = true

[dependencies.iced_highlighter]
workspace = true
optional = true

[dependencies.thiserror]
workspace = true

[dependencies.image]
workspace = true
optional = true

[profile.release-opt]
inherits = "release"
codegen-units = 1
debug = false
lto = true
incremental = false
opt-level = 3
overflow-checks = false
strip = "debuginfo"

[workspace.package]
version = "0.12.0"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[workspace.dependencies]
async-std = "1.0"
bitflags = "1.0"
cosmic-text = "0.10"
futures = "0.3"
glam = "0.24"
glyphon = "0.5"
guillotiere = "0.6"
half = "2.2"
image = "0.24"
kamadak-exif = "0.5"
kurbo = "0.9"
log = "0.4"
lyon = "1.0"
lyon_path = "1.0"
num-traits = "0.2"
once_cell = "1.0"
ouroboros = "0.17"
palette = "0.7"
raw-window-handle = "0.6"
resvg = "0.36"
rustc-hash = "1.0"
smol = "1.0"
smol_str = "0.2"
softbuffer = "0.4"
syntect = "5.1"
sysinfo = "0.28"
thiserror = "1.0"
tiny-skia = "0.11"
tokio = "1.0"
tracing = "0.1"
unicode-segmentation = "1.0"
wasm-bindgen-futures = "0.4"
wasm-timer = "0.2"
web-sys = "0.3"
web-time = "0.2"
wgpu = "0.19"
winapi = "0.3"
window_clipboard = "0.4"

[workspace.dependencies.iced]
version = "0.12"
path = "."

[workspace.dependencies.iced_core]
version = "0.12"
path = "core"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_futures]
version = "0.12"
path = "futures"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_graphics]
version = "0.12"
path = "graphics"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_highlighter]
version = "0.12"
path = "highlighter"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_renderer]
version = "0.12"
path = "renderer"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_runtime]
version = "0.12"
path = "runtime"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_style]
version = "0.12"
path = "style"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_tiny_skia]
version = "0.12"
path = "tiny_skia"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_wgpu]
version = "0.12"
path = "wgpu"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_widget]
version = "0.12"
path = "widget"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_winit]
version = "0.12"
path = "winit"

[workspace.dependencies.bytemuck]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[workspace.dependencies.qrcode]
version = "0.12"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.xxhash-rust]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "xxh3",]

[workspace.dependencies.winit]
git = "https://github.com/iced-rs/winit.git"
rev = "b91e39ece2c0d378c3b80da7f3ab50e17bb798a5"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
all-features = true

[package]
name = "iced_core"
description = "The essential ideas of iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1.0"
log = "0.4"
num-traits = "0.2"
smol_str = "0.2"
thiserror = "1.0"
web-time = "0.2"

[dev-dependencies]
approx = "0.5"

[dependencies.xxhash-rust]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "xxh3",]

[dependencies.palette]
optional = true
version = "0.7"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies]
raw-window-handle = "0.6"

[package]
name = "iced_futures"
description = "Commands, subscriptions, and future executors for iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
thread-pool = [ "futures/thread-pool",]

[dependencies]
futures = "0.3"
log = "0.4"

[dependencies.iced_core]
version = "0.12"
path = "core"

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies]
wasm-bindgen-futures = "0.4"
wasm-timer = "0.2"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
all-features = true

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.async-std]
optional = true
features = [ "unstable",]
version = "1.0"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.smol]
optional = true
version = "1.0"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.tokio]
optional = true
features = [ "rt", "rt-multi-thread", "time",]
version = "1.0"

[package]
name = "iced_graphics"
description = "A bunch of backend-agnostic types that can be leveraged to build a renderer for iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
geometry = [ "lyon_path",]
image = [ "dep:image", "kamadak-exif",]
web-colors = []

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1.0"
cosmic-text = "0.10"
glam = "0.24"
half = "2.2"
log = "0.4"
once_cell = "1.0"
raw-window-handle = "0.6"
rustc-hash = "1.0"
thiserror = "1.0"
unicode-segmentation = "1.0"

[dependencies.iced_core]
version = "0.12"
path = "core"

[dependencies.iced_futures]
version = "0.12"
path = "futures"

[dependencies.bytemuck]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.xxhash-rust]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "xxh3",]

[dependencies.image]
optional = true
version = "0.24"

[dependencies.kamadak-exif]
optional = true
version = "0.5"

[dependencies.lyon_path]
optional = true
version = "1.0"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
all-features = true

[package]
name = "iced_renderer"
description = "The official renderer for iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
wgpu = [ "iced_wgpu",]
image = [ "iced_tiny_skia/image", "iced_wgpu?/image",]
svg = [ "iced_tiny_skia/svg", "iced_wgpu?/svg",]
geometry = [ "iced_graphics/geometry", "iced_tiny_skia/geometry", "iced_wgpu?/geometry",]
tracing = [ "iced_wgpu?/tracing",]
web-colors = [ "iced_wgpu?/web-colors",]
webgl = [ "iced_wgpu?/webgl",]

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"
thiserror = "1.0"

[dependencies.iced_graphics]
version = "0.12"
path = "graphics"

[dependencies.iced_tiny_skia]
version = "0.12"
path = "tiny_skia"

[dependencies.iced_wgpu]
optional = true
version = "0.12"
path = "wgpu"

[package]
name = "iced_runtime"
description = "A renderer-agnostic runtime for iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
debug = []
multi-window = []

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1.0"

[dependencies.iced_core]
version = "0.12"
path = "core"

[dependencies.iced_futures]
features = [ "thread-pool",]
version = "0.12"
path = "futures"

[package]
name = "iced_style"
description = "The default set of styles of Iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[dependencies]
palette = "0.7"
once_cell = "1.0"

[dependencies.iced_core]
features = [ "palette",]
version = "0.12"
path = "core"

[package]
name = "iced_tiny_skia"
description = "A software renderer for iced on top of tiny-skia"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
image = [ "iced_graphics/image",]
svg = [ "resvg",]
geometry = [ "iced_graphics/geometry",]

[dependencies]
cosmic-text = "0.10"
kurbo = "0.9"
log = "0.4"
rustc-hash = "1.0"
softbuffer = "0.4"
tiny-skia = "0.11"

[dependencies.iced_graphics]
version = "0.12"
path = "graphics"

[dependencies.bytemuck]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.xxhash-rust]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "xxh3",]

[dependencies.resvg]
optional = true
version = "0.36"

[package]
name = "iced_wgpu"
description = "A renderer for iced on top of wgpu"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
geometry = [ "iced_graphics/geometry", "lyon",]
image = [ "iced_graphics/image",]
svg = [ "resvg",]
web-colors = [ "iced_graphics/web-colors",]
webgl = [ "wgpu/webgl",]

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1.0"
futures = "0.3"
glam = "0.24"
glyphon = "0.5"
guillotiere = "0.6"
log = "0.4"
once_cell = "1.0"
wgpu = "0.19"

[dependencies.iced_graphics]
version = "0.12"
path = "graphics"

[dependencies.bytemuck]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.lyon]
optional = true
version = "1.0"

[dependencies.resvg]
optional = true
version = "0.36"

[dependencies.tracing]
optional = true
version = "0.1"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
all-features = true

[package]
name = "iced_widget"
description = "The built-in widgets for iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
lazy = [ "ouroboros",]
image = [ "iced_renderer/image",]
svg = [ "iced_renderer/svg",]
canvas = [ "iced_renderer/geometry",]
qr_code = [ "canvas", "qrcode",]
wgpu = [ "iced_renderer/wgpu",]

[dependencies]
num-traits = "0.2"
thiserror = "1.0"
unicode-segmentation = "1.0"

[dependencies.iced_renderer]
version = "0.12"
path = "renderer"

[dependencies.iced_runtime]
version = "0.12"
path = "runtime"

[dependencies.iced_style]
version = "0.12"
path = "style"

[dependencies.ouroboros]
optional = true
version = "0.17"

[dependencies.qrcode]
optional = true
version = "0.12"
default-features = false

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
all-features = true

[package]
name = "iced_winit"
description = "A runtime for iced on top of winit"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
default = [ "x11", "wayland", "wayland-dlopen", "wayland-csd-adwaita",]
debug = [ "iced_runtime/debug",]
system = [ "sysinfo",]
application = []
x11 = [ "winit/x11",]
wayland = [ "winit/wayland",]
wayland-dlopen = [ "winit/wayland-dlopen",]
wayland-csd-adwaita = [ "winit/wayland-csd-adwaita",]
multi-window = [ "iced_runtime/multi-window",]

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"
thiserror = "1.0"
tracing = "0.1"
window_clipboard = "0.4"

[dependencies.iced_graphics]
version = "0.12"
path = "graphics"

[dependencies.iced_runtime]
version = "0.12"
path = "runtime"

[dependencies.iced_style]
version = "0.12"
path = "style"

[dependencies.winit]
git = "https://github.com/iced-rs/winit.git"
rev = "b91e39ece2c0d378c3b80da7f3ab50e17bb798a5"

[dependencies.sysinfo]
optional = true
version = "0.28"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies]
winapi = "0.3"

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.web-sys]
features = [ "Document", "Window",]
version = "0.3"

[package]
name = "winit"
version = "0.29.10"
authors = [ "The winit contributors", "Pierre Krieger <pierre.krieger1708@gmail.com>",]
description = "Cross-platform window creation library."
edition = "2021"
keywords = [ "windowing",]
license = "Apache-2.0"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/rust-windowing/winit"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/winit"
categories = [ "gui",]
rust-version = "1.65.0"

[features]
default = [ "rwh_06", "x11", "wayland", "wayland-dlopen", "wayland-csd-adwaita",]
x11 = [ "x11-dl", "bytemuck", "percent-encoding", "xkbcommon-dl/x11", "x11rb",]
wayland = [ "wayland-client", "wayland-backend", "wayland-protocols", "wayland-protocols-plasma", "sctk", "ahash", "memmap2",]
wayland-dlopen = [ "wayland-backend/dlopen",]
wayland-csd-adwaita = [ "sctk-adwaita", "sctk-adwaita/ab_glyph",]
wayland-csd-adwaita-crossfont = [ "sctk-adwaita", "sctk-adwaita/crossfont",]
wayland-csd-adwaita-notitle = [ "sctk-adwaita",]
android-native-activity = [ "android-activity/native-activity",]
android-game-activity = [ "android-activity/game-activity",]
serde = [ "dep:serde", "cursor-icon/serde", "smol_str/serde",]
rwh_04 = [ "dep:rwh_04", "ndk/rwh_04",]
rwh_05 = [ "dep:rwh_05", "ndk/rwh_05",]
rwh_06 = [ "dep:rwh_06", "ndk/rwh_06",]

[build-dependencies]
cfg_aliases = "0.1.1"

[dependencies]
bitflags = "2"
cursor-icon = "1.1.0"
log = "0.4"
once_cell = "1.12"
smol_str = "0.2.0"

[workspace]
members = [ "run-wasm",]

[dependencies.mint]
version = "0.5.6"
optional = true

[dependencies.rwh_04]
package = "raw-window-handle"
version = "0.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.rwh_05]
package = "raw-window-handle"
version = "0.5.2"
features = [ "std",]
optional = true

[dependencies.rwh_06]
package = "raw-window-handle"
version = "0.6"
features = [ "std",]
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
optional = true
features = [ "serde_derive",]

[dev-dependencies.image]
version = "0.24.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "png",]

[dev-dependencies.simple_logger]
version = "4.2.0"
default_features = false

[dev-dependencies.winit]
path = "."
features = [ "rwh_05",]

[target."cfg(not(any(target_os = \"android\", target_os = \"ios\")))".dev-dependencies]
softbuffer = "0.3.0"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"android\")".dependencies]
android-activity = "0.5.0"
ndk-sys = "0.5.0"

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \"ios\", target_os = \"macos\"))".dependencies]
core-foundation = "0.9.3"
objc2 = "0.4.1"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies]
core-graphics = "0.23.1"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies]
unicode-segmentation = "1.7.1"

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os = \"redox\", target_family = \"wasm\", target_os = \"android\", target_os = \"ios\", target_os = \"macos\"))))".dependencies]
calloop = "0.12.3"
libc = "0.2.64"
xkbcommon-dl = "0.4.0"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"redox\")".dependencies]
redox_syscall = "0.3"

[target."cfg(target_family = \"wasm\")".dependencies]
atomic-waker = "1"
js-sys = "0.3.64"
wasm-bindgen = "0.2"
wasm-bindgen-futures = "0.4"
web-time = "0.2"

[target."cfg(target_family = \"wasm\")".dev-dependencies]
console_log = "1"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "rwh_04", "rwh_05", "rwh_06", "serde", "android-native-activity",]
default-target = "x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu"
targets = [ "i686-pc-windows-msvc", "x86_64-pc-windows-msvc", "x86_64-apple-darwin", "i686-unknown-linux-gnu", "x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu", "x86_64-apple-ios", "aarch64-linux-android", "wasm32-unknown-unknown",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"android\")".dependencies.ndk]
version = "0.8.0"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.icrate]
version = "0.0.4"
features = [ "dispatch", "Foundation", "Foundation_NSArray", "Foundation_NSAttributedString", "Foundation_NSMutableAttributedString", "Foundation_NSData", "Foundation_NSDictionary", "Foundation_NSString", "Foundation_NSProcessInfo", "Foundation_NSThread", "Foundation_NSNumber",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"ios\")".dependencies.icrate]
version = "0.0.4"
features = [ "dispatch", "Foundation", "Foundation_NSArray", "Foundation_NSString", "Foundation_NSProcessInfo", "Foundation_NSThread", "Foundation_NSSet",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.windows-sys]
version = "0.48"
features = [ "Win32_Devices_HumanInterfaceDevice", "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Globalization", "Win32_Graphics_Dwm", "Win32_Graphics_Gdi", "Win32_Media", "Win32_System_Com_StructuredStorage", "Win32_System_Com", "Win32_System_LibraryLoader", "Win32_System_Ole", "Win32_System_SystemInformation", "Win32_System_SystemServices", "Win32_System_Threading", "Win32_System_WindowsProgramming", "Win32_UI_Accessibility", "Win32_UI_Controls", "Win32_UI_HiDpi", "Win32_UI_Input_Ime", "Win32_UI_Input_KeyboardAndMouse", "Win32_UI_Input_Pointer", "Win32_UI_Input_Touch", "Win32_UI_Shell", "Win32_UI_TextServices", "Win32_UI_WindowsAndMessaging",]

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os = \"redox\", target_family = \"wasm\", target_os = \"android\", target_os = \"ios\", target_os = \"macos\"))))".dependencies.ahash]
version = "0.8.3"
features = [ "no-rng",]
optional = true

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os = \"redox\", target_family = \"wasm\", target_os = \"android\", target_os = \"ios\", target_os = \"macos\"))))".dependencies.bytemuck]
version = "1.13.1"
default-features = false
optional = true

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os = \"redox\", target_family = \"wasm\", target_os = \"android\", target_os = \"ios\", target_os = \"macos\"))))".dependencies.memmap2]
version = "0.9.0"
optional = true

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os = \"redox\", target_family = \"wasm\", target_os = \"android\", target_os = \"ios\", target_os = \"macos\"))))".dependencies.percent-encoding]
version = "2.0"
optional = true

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os = \"redox\", target_family = \"wasm\", target_os = \"android\", target_os = \"ios\", target_os = \"macos\"))))".dependencies.rustix]
